Output Valid CFB Team Names and Abbreviations

Source: R/utils.R
valid_team_names.Rd

Output Valid CFB Team Names and Abbreviations

valid_team_names(
  division = c("FBS", "P5", "G5", "FCS", "DII", "DIII", "Conference", "hoopR", "Other")
)
